{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "title": "command_injection.time_based",
  "description": "Command injection proven by a latency delta from an injected shell sleep (control/low/high).",
  "x-flags": "(http/timing — no extra flag)",
  "x-notes": [
    "The engine builds control/low/high by planting each payloads value into injection.location of base_request; the arms differ only in that one slot.",
    "payloads.control is the uninjected value; delay_low/delay_high carry a small vs large shell sleep. kind=query|form needs name; json_body needs json_pointer.",
    "Set min_median_delta_ms below the real sleep, above noise; floor is 3000. Unstable targets map to Inconclusive.",
    "If proof.timeout_ms is set it must exceed the expected high-arm delay; a high arm that sleeps longer errors and yields Inconclusive (fail-safe), never a false Verified or NotReproduced."
  ],
  "type": "object",
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "required": ["finding_id", "type", "target", "evidence", "proof"],
  "properties": {
    "finding_id": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
    "type": { "const": "command_injection.time_based" },
    "target": { "$ref": "#/$defs/target" },
    "auth": { "$ref": "#/$defs/auth" },
    "controls": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/request" } },
    "mutation_slots": { "$ref": "#/$defs/mutation_slots" },
    "side_effects": { "$ref": "#/$defs/side_effects" },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["base_request", "injection"],
      "properties": {
        "base_request": { "$ref": "#/$defs/request" },
        "injection": {
          "allOf": [{ "$ref": "#/$defs/injection" }],
          "properties": {
            "payloads": {
              "required": ["control", "delay_low", "delay_high"]
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "proof": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "properties": {
        "repetitions": { "type": "number" },
        "min_median_delta_ms": { "type": "number" },
        "require_body_similarity": { "type": "boolean" }
      }
    }
  },
  "examples": [
    {
      "finding_id": "cmdi-timing-ping",
      "type": "command_injection.time_based",
      "target": {
        "expected_origin": "https://app.example.com",
        "allowed_hosts": ["app.example.com"],
        "allowed_schemes": ["https"],
        "allowed_ports": [443]
      },
      "auth": { "required": false },
      "evidence": {
        "base_request": { "method": "GET", "url": "https://app.example.com/ping?host=127.0.0.1" },
        "injection": {
          "location": { "kind": "query", "name": "host" },
          "payloads": {
            "control": "127.0.0.1",
            "delay_low": "127.0.0.1;sleep 0",
            "delay_high": "127.0.0.1;sleep 5"
          }
        }
      },
      "proof": {
        "repetitions": 5,
        "min_median_delta_ms": 3500,
        "require_body_similarity": true
      }
    }
  ]
}
